result.adr_address: 32 Wyndham St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Stockton

reviews.text: Slightly hidden away and hard to find cocktail bar on Wyndham. Well worth looking for it as they really have excellent cocktails and a really good atmosphere. Classics like their Negroni, and Old Fashioned are done really well, and they some really interesting gin cocktails.
Classic bar. Drinks are good, but not very much creative. Atmosphere is dark and classy, reminiscent of an English gentleman’s club. Nice.
A true classic bar. Drinks are a science here. the atmosphere is nice. I had a very good time with my local colleagues.

Waitress was extremely rude and spent most of her time hanging around the bar, basically impossible to get her attention. A waiter also came over and grabbed our menu without saying anything. This is probably the most disappointing bar I've ever seen in Hong Kong.
This bar is hard to find. The cocktails are very special with rare ingredients and flavors. Beautiful interior and jazz music make the stay perfect.
